(firstQuint)Phase II Study of Pre-Operative Chemotherapy in Patients With Resectable Local-Regional Carcinoma of Esophagus.

 This study is designed for patients with resectable, local-regional carcinoma of the esophagus.

 In a pre-operative setting, chemotherapy with Taxol, Cisplatin, and 5-Fluorouracil will be administered followed by G-CSF.

